## How to Run the Game

```bash
cd Robina-AsteroidsGame/Robina-AsteroidsGame
mvn clean install
mvn -pl Core javafx:run

--- 

## How to Run the Microservice

```bash
cd AsteroidsGame
mvn spring-boot:run

Access the service via:
http://localhost:8080